## pre requirement

1) tools 
BWA (mapper)
SAMTOOLS (for sorting)
MACS2 (peak calling)
HOMER (annotation and tables)

2) genome index for mapping

the index steps is not included, i think it is better that way.


## how to

0) before using the sakefile, change the json configration file

1) snakefile for data with no input
snakemake -s Snakefile_no_control --configfile srr4004173_config_no_control.json

2) snakefile for data with input
snakemake -s Snakefile_with_control --configfile srr4004173_config_with_control.json

